Scott Neal

Scott Neal is the president of D. Scott Neal, Inc. He holds MBA and Master of Divinity degrees and has concentrated his service in the areas of estate, retirement and investment planning since 1986. He is a CPA  and a Certified Financial Planner. 
Because he works frequently with owners of small and medium sized businesses, Scott became a Theory of Constraints Jonah and a Certified Exit Planning Advisor. 
Scott has been selected multiple times by Medical Economics magazine as one of the countryâs Best Financial Advisors for Doctors. He is a voracious reader and a sought-after speaker. 
Scott will address questions regarding any aspect of the firmâs services. Call him at (800) 344-9098 or reach him by e-mail at scott@dsneal.com.




 

