About Us

What is your greatest financial concern right now?  As fee-only financial planners we provide sound analysis and recommendations that are in your best interest. We hold ourselves to a fiduciary standard always.  


How We Got Started

As a CPA, my mind tired of looking back and accounting for what happened last year.  An assessment of my strengths revealed that my brain is energized by looking forward--into the future.  Coupled with a talent for strategic thinking, I began making coherence out of chaos for our clients.  Our clients and I both became much happier.  


Our Ideal Customer

Specifically looking for boomers who are now caring for a parent or might be called upon to become a caregiver in the future.  We have a program called Partnering with my Parent.  It also works for boomers who want to plan for their own future. 





Our Team








